\newlabel{fig:input_optimization}{{4}{10}{Model-guided optimization of vineyard plant-protection inputs in GrapeMaster. Weather records, cultivar data, soil and field information, and agrochemical master data are integrated within the crop-season analytical workflow to support input selection, application timing, spray-frequency reduction, and dose optimization}{figure.4}{}}
