\newlabel{fig:task_management_interfaces}{{10}{17}{Task-management and plant-protection input interfaces: (a) task list with pending and completed operations, (b) fungicide and pesticide product selection, and (c) sprayer-tank mixing and dosage calculation}{figure.10}{}}
