\newlabel{fig:ai_diagnosis_interfaces}{{11}{19}{AI-assisted disease consultation interfaces in GrapeMaster. The mobile workflow supports field-image submission, guided question selection, and advisory responses that combine visible symptom information with disease-prevention and crop-management recommendations}{figure.11}{}}
